title: I Really Don’t Want to Learn Forbidden Spells
description: I Really Don’t Want to Learn Forbidden Spells Manhua I admit, when it comes to time travel, there must be some sort of cheat code. But seriously, which newbie mage only knows dark curses like “forbidden spells”? I’m human, not a dark lord! Oh well, I guess forbidden spells are pretty cool after all! I Really Don’t Want to Learn Forbidden Spells | Wǒ Zhēn Bù Xiǎng Xué Jìn Zhòu | 我真不想学禁咒
alternative_titles: I Really Don’t Want to Learn Forbidden Spells
